choices.text:
when I was 6, my sister was half my age. Now I am 80. How old is my sister now? Calculate this step by step.
When you were 6 your sister's age was half of yours which means she was three years old. When you are 80 that would mean your sister is 79, but it also means she has aged a year in the past few years so she should be 80 now.
